Description:
A Point in the Right Direction
A glorious 2 bedroom apartment awaits the discerning buyer, either to move in or rent out straight away. Located in the renowned Elenberg Fraser Watergate residential complex, its’ central location is perfect. With the quietest living around due to its unique aerodynamic tower design, come and see why so many residents love living here!
Beautifully spacious apartment with large open plan dining and living area adjoins East facing balcony to take in the City skyline views. Across to the South you will be greeted with picturesque views over Docklands Park. A stylish kitchen with stone bench tops incorporates an island bench, great for food preparation, as well as integrated stainless steel appliances including Gas stove, electric oven and dishwasher. Main bedroom with ensuite and study alcove. Mirrored built in robes to both bedrooms. Fully tiled Central dual access bathroom with laundry area.
Additional features to this lovely apartment include: ducted heating and cooling, secured entrance, onsite building manager, double glazed floor to ceiling windows and cross ventilation, one undercover car space.
Building facilities include: 3 lane heated lap pool with spa, gymnasium, sauna and function room.
This is a wonderful opportunity to live right in the heart of Docklands, close to Southern Cross Station, located within the Free Tram Zone, walking distance to an abundance of great cafes and restaurants, and everything you could possibly need.

In the Heart of Docklands Surrounded by Water Views
On offer is this top floor apartment in the Striking EXO residential complex.
2 bedrooms with mirrored robes, main with private balcony, share the central stylish bathroom.
The large kitchen with an island bench provides terrific space for food preparation and ease of cooking. Highlighted by LED feature lighting, ample storage and integrated stainless steel appliances.
Large open plan living and dining area adjoins a massive sheltered balcony perfect for outdoor entertaining and BBQ dining.

- Free Tram Zone and Capital City Bike Trail at your door
- Easy access to Southern Cross Station and Melbourne's Freeway Network

Description:
When Size Matters, 149sqm Pad with Dual CBD & Harbour Views!
Simple in design yet spectacular in scope, this leading-edge 2 bedroom, 2 bathroom apartment sets a noteworthy benchmark for contemporary Docklands living. From the sprawling, distinctive and open floorplan to the pair of full-width balconies showcasing uninterrupted city and harbour views day and night, this is superior Docklands living with all the lifestyle benefits.
Prominently positioned on the 33rd floor of the tightly held Victoria Point tower, discover oversized living and dining alongside a stone-topped kitchen with a full suite of high-end Miele appliances and an entertainers' island bench. Sensationally book-ended by two large balconies, leading off the huge master suite with parents retreat one terrace sweeps across the magnificent Melbourne skyline from the city to Port Phillip Bay, the other reveals the special tranquillity of Victoria Harbour framed by Docklands Stadium, the Melbourne Star and West Gate Bridge.
Set over an impressive 149m2 (approx.) inside and out, enjoy a separate laundry, two side by side parking spaces plus storage cage, intercom entry, ducted heating/cooling, concierge, and access to gym.
Please call Cary Thornton on 0481 010 740 for an inspection

Description:
LUXURY AT IT’S BEST
Discover absolute waterfront living with this luxury 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom plus study apartment. Set in the Yarra Point development located in the Yarra's Edge Precinct which has irresistible marina and city views. The apartment offers accommodation in abundance - perfect for families or those looking to downsize without compromising on size. It is in immediate proximity to South Wharf retail and Crown entertainment precincts, Melbourne CBD and The Yarra’s Edge RekDek fitness facilities.
The apartment has a large open-plan north-facing space for relaxing, dining and entertaining. The kitchen flows effortlessly to a balcony that captures outlooks over the surrounding wonderland.
The master bedroom suite is an idyllic retreat with its personal balcony, built-in robes and lavish ensuite with bath, separate shower and double vanities. Built-in robes are fitted in the two minor bedrooms and a desk is integrated into the study. Two adjoining parallel car spaces and laundry heighten the appeal.
For inspection call Glenn Donnelly on 0419 998 235

Description:
Perfectly located, endless source of entertainment and leisure activities
The apartment showcases elegant and modern kitchen with marble stone bench tops, quality stainless steel appliances and a breakfast bar. Each unit comprises of spacious living area with floor to ceiling double glazed windows which enhances the experience and minimize heat intrusion. An undeniable focus on cosmopolitan design is highlighted with vogue mosaic shower tiles and integrated European laundry. The private balcony is definitely an amazing area for you to enjoy the view and relax at. Bedrooms are being fitted with mirrored built-in robes.
Located just moments away from Etihad Stadium, Southern Cross Station, Docklands shopping precinct and Docklands bars and restaurants, you will never be short of things to do! A tram stop right at your doorstep and just 0.5km away from Southern Cross Station. Well serviced by Melbourne’s extensive tram and road network, you can easily access to Melbourne CBD or any other! By tram, the City Circle Tram provides free transport on the corner of Harbour Esplanade and Bourke Street west. Within walking distance, you can explore Docklands Waterfront and Harbour Town shopping Centre. Perfectly located, it offers endless source of entertainment and leisure activities.
All residents will have access to a wide range of facilities which includes:
• Full sized swimming pool
• Gymnasium
• Sauna
• Lounge/ Function Area
Location:

• 800m to Spencer Outlet
• 800m to South Wharf Promenade
• 1.9km to Flinders Station
• 2.1km to Crown Casino

Welcome to some of the best views in Melbourne
This 112 sqm internal apartment which also has 23 sqm of balcony space is located in the Heart of Docklands. The apartment stunningly captures views of the CBD, Yarra River, Port Philip Bay, and beautiful night time Crown Casino fire shows. With a large central living area providing more than ample space for modern inner city living and massive wrap around balcony perfect for entertaining, you would be hard pressed to find a more appealing apartment in Melbourne. This apartment is perfectly priced and located for anyone who enjoys spacious modern living in a great location.

Simple in design yet spectacular in scope, this leading-edge 2 bedroom, 2 bathroom apartment sets a noteworthy benchmark for contemporary Docklands living. From the sprawling, distinctive and open floorplan to the pair of full-width balconies showcasing uninterrupted city and harbour views day and night, this is superior Docklands living with all the lifestyle benefits.

Description:
UNDER OFFER - Loft Style Living with Stunning Vistas
With a fantastic position this excellent private segment of Village Docklands, this unique dual level one bedroom apartment offers light-filled and spacious loft-style living with superb indoor/outdoor flexibility. Enjoying a south-east orientation, this 3rd floor residence is the perfect choice for first home buyers, CBD professionals or smart investors who can enjoy solid returns.
The central lounge and dining zone bathed in natural light features, carpet floors and full windows which opening out to the balcony where residents can soak in the sun. The stone kitchen enjoys a mirrored splashback and stainless steel appliances, while the upstairs bedroom comes with a stylish ensuite bathroom.
The many extras include a European laundry, reverse cycle cooling, video intercom entry, 4 x storage cages, and access to gym, outdoor pool, and BBQ courtyard and garden area. Moments to South Wharf, DFO shopping, Crown Casino and Southbank, Etihad Stadium, Docklands Park, trams at your door, and Southern Cross Station.
Please contact Vicky Leong on 0452 486 860 to arrange an exclusive viewing.

Description:
SOLID RETURNS & SELLING WITH ALL FURNISHINGS
Situated high up on the 9th floor of the popular Lacrosse building is this well kept 2 bedroom residence. Furniture displayed will be sold with the apartment giving it added value in a high demand furnished rental Docklands market.
Featuring:
- 2 bedrooms with built in robes, master with ensuite access
- Additional bathroom with European laundry space with included washing machine
- Spacious open plan living and dining area with floor to ceiling windows and direct access to your very own entertainers undercover balcony
- Endless kitchen cupboard space and storage with stainless steel appliances including gas cook top range hood and dishwasher. Fridge will also be included in sale.
- Split system heating and cooling
- Access to gym and pool
Location:
- Moments away to Harbour Town shopping centre, Etihad stadium and the CBD
- City Circle tram at your door step as well as Southern Cross station only 2 minutes walk away
- Easy access to freeways, Docklands harbour, shops cafes and restaurants
If you are looking for central city pad ready to be enjoyed or looking for a solid cash flow investment with current rental yield of $550 per week (with potential to yield up to $600 pw), this apartment could be for you. There are endless earning opportunities with this apartment as the Docklands furnished and short stay rental market are in high demand especially in peak period during major events and holiday periods where nightly stays can return up to $200 a night.

Description:
An Inspired High Rise Docklands Sensation within Minutes to South Wharf
With breathtaking views of the renowned Yarra’s Edge marina and Melbourne CBD, this immaculate owner occupied residence is an outstanding opportunity for the most fastidious of buyers.
With a spacious central living zone this apartment promotes an expansive lounge and dining area, an exquisite kitchen with feature island bench, clever storage plus stainless steel Miele appliances including a dishwasher and gas cook top. All of this is beautifully framed by floor to ceiling windows and an undercover balcony, capturing the marvellous views of the marina, Southbank and beyond.
The sizeable master suite is completed with a walk-in robe and deluxe ensuite, while a 2nd bedroom with built-in robe, third bedroom/home office, impressive central bathroom, and separate laundry are further highlights. Other extras include ducted heating and cooling, secure intercom, storage cage, and 2 secure car spaces. Residents have access to an on-site gym as well as RekDek which includes a gym, pool, spa, steam room, and sauna.
For those who want to live the amazing Docklands lifestyle, this one is for you. Hitting lively South Wharf restaurants will become part of your weekend routine, with Bangpop, The General Assembly, and Akachochin Japanese restaurant accessible within a few minutes’ walk, not to mention premium shopping within South Wharf DFO. You’re also not far from Crown Entertainment Complex, Capital City Trail, Spencer Street trams, and Southern Cross Station.
